      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "人の真似をするのも、別に悪くはないんだけどな\nただ、それ自体が目的になっちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not necessarily bad to imitate others\nBut it shouldn't be the sole purpose",
