      "startTime": 257.7333432514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "大事なのは、立派なセンターになることじゃなくて\nライブでお客さんを楽しませることだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The important thing isn't just becoming a great center.\nIt's about entertaining the audience at the live‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.5666806537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr027.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね\n私、一番肝心なところが抜けてたみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right\nI seemed to have missed the most important point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.3666806537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr028.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットのみんなとライブに出るのは凄く楽しみだし\n絶対に成功させたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really looking forward to performing with everyone at the unit‚\nand I absolutely want it to be a success",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.6000200906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr029.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そのために何をしたらいいのか……\n……ダメですね、私、全然分からないままで",
      "translations": {
